cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.CR 

This paper is primarily focused on face recognition, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) category. The paper also extensively uses deep neural network techniques (cs.LG) and proposes a new learning method (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper deals with large scale face databases (cs.MM) and proposes a method to enhance the discrimination capability of face features (cs.CR).
